  "texts": [
    "Transferring information from learned tasks to new tasks with few examples increases classification performance [39].Here, a pre-trained ResNet18 network with ImageNet dataset was used.",
    "Then, the obtained model was fine-tuned on the BUSI dataset with the transfer learning approach.",
    "For this, the images were converted to the input size of the ResNet18 network.",
    "The hyperparameters are as follows: learning rate 0.001, minibatch size 16 and 300 epochs.",
    "This model was used as a baseline for comparison purposes and achieved an accuracy of 0.831.Tables 4 and 5 present the accuracy achieved in the 3-way classification of the BUSI dataset using different backbones and two meta-learning algorithms for various shot values during meta-training with the mini-ImageNet and BreakHis datasets, respectively."
  ],
